CMV_CRONTAB_EXPRESSION_TIP.zh:
cron表达式

cron表达式被用来配置CronTrigger(org.quartz.Trigger的一个子类)。cron表达式由7个子表达式组成，这些子表达式分别描述了cron表达式所代表的的时间集的不同方面。

这些由空格分隔的子表达式可以由任何表达式规则允许的值，字段或是组合构成。表A-1按顺序介绍了这些字段。

表A-1 Cron表达式允许的值和字段

名称 必填 合法值 合法特殊字符

秒

是

0-59

, - * /

分钟

是

0-59

, - * /

小时

是

0-23

, - * /

月中此日

是

1-31

, - * ? / L W C

月份

是

0-11 or JAN-DEC

, - * /

周中此日

是

1-7 or SUN-SAT

, - * ? / L C #

年份

否

empty or 1970-2099

, - * /

示例 A-1 Cron表达式

Cron表达式可以简单如 * * * * ? * 亦可复杂如 0 0/5 14,18,3-39,52 ? JAN,MAR,SEP MON-FRI 2002-2010。

更多示例:

表达式 含义
0 0 12 * * ? 每日中午12点触发
0 15 10 ? * * 每日上午10:15触发
0 15 10 * * ? 每日上午10:15触发
0 15 10 * * ? * 每日上午10:15触发
0 15 10 * * ? 2005 2005年中的每日上午10:15触发
0 * 14 * * ? 每日下午2:00至2:59的每分钟均触发
0 0/5 14 * * ? 每日下午2:00至2:55的每5分钟均触发
0 0/5 14,18 * * ? 每日下午2:00至2:55、6:00至6:55的每5分钟均触发
0 0-5 14 * * ? 每日下午2:00至2:05的每分钟均触发
0 10,44 14 ? 3 WED 三月中每周三下午2:10及2:44均触发
0 15 10 ? * MON-FRI 每周一至五的上午10:15均触发
0 15 10 15 * ? 每月15日上午10:15均触发
0 15 10 L * ? 每月最后一日上午10:15均触发
0 15 10 ? * 6L 每月最后一个周五上午10:15均触发
0 15 10 ? * 6L 每月最后一个周五上午10:15均触发
0 15 10 ? * 6L 2002-2005 2002-2005年每月最后一个周五上午10:15均触发
0 15 10 ? * 6#3 每月第三个周五上午10:15均触发
0 0 12 1/5 * ? 从每月第一天开始，每五天的中午12点均触发
0 11 11 11 11 ? 每个十一月11日上午11:11均触发
CMV_CRONTAB_EXPRESSION_TIP.en:
A Cron Expressions

Cron expressions are used to configure instances of CronTrigger, a subclass of org.quartz.Trigger. A cron expression is a string consisting of six or seven subexpressions (fields) that describe individual details of the schedule.

These fields, separated by white space, can contain any of the allowed values with various combinations of the allowed characters for that field. Table A-1 shows the fields in the expected order.

Table A-1 Cron Expressions Allowed Fields and Values

Name Required Allowed Values Allowed Special Characters

Seconds

Y

0-59

, - * /

Minutes

Y

0-59

, - * /

Hours

Y

0-23

, - * /

Day of month

Y

1-31

, - * ? / L W C

Month

Y

0-11 or JAN-DEC

, - * /

Day of week

Y

1-7 or SUN-SAT

, - * ? / L C #

Year

N

empty or 1970-2099

, - * /

Example A-1 Cron Expressions

Cron expressions can be as simple as * * * * ? * or as complex as 0 0/5 14,18,3-39,52 ? JAN,MAR,SEP MON-FRI 2002-2010.

Here are some more examples:

Expression Means
0 0 12 * * ? Fire at 12:00 PM (noon) every day
0 15 10 ? * * Fire at 10:15 AM every day
0 15 10 * * ? Fire at 10:15 AM every day
0 15 10 * * ? * Fire at 10:15 AM every day
0 15 10 * * ? 2005 Fire at 10:15 AM every day during the year 2005
0 * 14 * * ? Fire every minute starting at 2:00 PM and ending at 2:59 PM, every day
0 0/5 14 * * ? Fire every 5 minutes starting at 2:00 PM and ending at 2:55 PM, every day
0 0/5 14,18 * * ? Fire every 5 minutes starting at 2:00 PM and ending at 2:55 PM, AND fire every 5 minutes starting at 6:00 PM and ending at 6:55 PM, every day
0 0-5 14 * * ? Fire every minute starting at 2:00 PM and ending at 2:05 PM, every day
0 10,44 14 ? 3 WED Fire at 2:10 PM and at 2:44 PM every Wednesday in the month of March
0 15 10 ? * MON-FRI Fire at 10:15 AM every Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday and Friday
0 15 10 15 * ? Fire at 10:15 AM on the 15th day of every month
0 15 10 L * ? Fire at 10:15 AM on the last day of every month
0 15 10 ? * 6L Fire at 10:15 AM on the last Friday of every month
0 15 10 ? * 6L Fire at 10:15 AM on the last Friday of every month
0 15 10 ? * 6L 2002-2005 Fire at 10:15 AM on every last friday of every month during the years 2002, 2003, 2004, and 2005
0 15 10 ? * 6#3 Fire at 10:15 AM on the third Friday of every month
0 0 12 1/5 * ? Fire at 12 PM (noon) every 5 days every month, starting on the first day of the month
0 11 11 11 11 ? Fire every November 11 at 11:11 AM
